casebody.data:
The District Board of Assessors et al. v. The State, ex rel. Morgan. Supreme court

Moot questions not determined.

(No. 14708 Decided July 20, 1915.) Error to Court of Appeals of Cuyahoga county. Mr. Timothy S. Hogan, attorney general, and Mr. Robert M. Morgan, for plaintiffs in error. Messrs. Dawley, Ewing, Counts & Terrell; Mr. Cyrus Locher, prosecuting attorney, and Mr. Frederick Green, assistant prosecuting attorney, for defendant in error.

Petition in error dismissed on authority of Minef v. Witt, 82 Ohio St., 237.

Nichols, C. J., Johnson, Donahue, Wanamaker, Newman, Jones and Matthias, JJ., concur.
